sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser as Orion Frontend
    participant Backend as Orion Backend
    participant TM as KeycloakTokenManager
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant RHAO as Red Hat Agent Operator
    participant Pod as Agent Pod

    Note over User,Browser: User initiates chat from Test tab
    User->>Browser: Send message to agent
    Browser->>Backend: POST /api/augment/chat/stream<br/>Cookie: backstage-auth<br/>X-Backstage-Request: augment

    Note over Backend: Identity Resolution
    Backend->>Backend: httpAuth.credentials(req)
    Backend->>Backend: userRef = user:default/alice

    Note over Backend,KC: Token Acquisition
    Backend->>TM: getTokenForStreaming(300000ms)
    TM->>TM: Check cached token

    alt Token valid and has enough lifetime
        TM-->>Backend: Cached token
    else Token expired or insufficient lifetime
        TM->>KC: POST /realms/kagenti/protocol/openid-connect/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>client_id=kagenti-api<br/>client_secret=***
        KC->>KC: Issue JWT with audience scopes
        Note over KC: JWT contains:<br/>aud: [spiffe://cluster/ns/sa/agent1, ...]<br/>azp: kagenti-api<br/>roles: [admin]
        KC-->>TM: {access_token, expires_in: 1800}
        TM->>TM: Cache token (expires_in - 60s buffer)
        TM-->>Backend: Fresh token
    end

    Note over Backend,Pod: Request to Agent
    Backend->>RHAO: POST /api/v1/chat/ns/agent/stream<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWT}<br/>X-Backstage-User: user:default/alice
    RHAO->>RHAO: Validate JWT signature + expiry
    RHAO->>Pod: Forward to agent (A2A protocol)

    Note over Pod: Agent Auth Validation
    Pod->>Pod: Validate JWT audience claim
    Pod->>Pod: Check: aud contains my SPIFFE ID?

    alt Audience matches
        Pod->>Pod: Process message with LLM
        Pod-->>RHAO: SSE: stream events
        RHAO-->>Backend: Forward SSE stream
        Backend-->>Browser: data: {type: stream.text.delta, delta: "..."}
    else Audience mismatch
        Pod-->>RHAO: 401 token validation failed
        RHAO-->>Backend: {error: auth.unauthorized}
        Backend-->>Browser: data: {type: stream.error, error: "Agent rejected token"}
    end

    Note over Backend: On 401 Response
    Backend->>TM: clearCache()
    Backend->>TM: getToken() (retry with fresh token)
